    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >烧脑又上头！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时间试炼》是一款适合全年龄的街机风格数字方块解谜游戏，让你的数学实力极速飞升！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/338a28427a4ebd7987db230a6e051e87.poster.avif?t=1765408980\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/338a28427a4ebd7987db230a6e051e87.webm?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/338a28427a4ebd7987db230a6e051e87.mp4?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标很简单：将不断下落的数字方块排列成横行或竖列，使它们的总和或乘积等于目标数字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但随着方块越来越快地下落，你需要迅雷不及掩耳的反应速度才能坚持下去！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >41种玩法任你选</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“计分模式”中争分夺秒，或在“谜题模式”中深思熟虑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从加法到代数，共有6到7种数学主题可选，总有一款适合你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是普通的数学，是“烧脑”的快乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/2c5ea522ac2155c6349c01345744f563.poster.avif?t=1765408980\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/2c5ea522ac2155c6349c01345744f563.webm?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/2c5ea522ac2155c6349c01345744f563.mp4?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全民皆可挑战！不管你是刚入门的数学萌新，还是人称“行走的计算器”，这款游戏都能满足你的需求。轻松练习？进阶挑战？《时间试炼》通通安排！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和朋友来场“数学大乱斗”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 对战模式上线，快乐翻倍！挑战你的朋友和家人，看看谁才是真·数学王者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/930b9bb53049b4fee3c270f1f989db43.poster.avif?t=1765408980\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/930b9bb53049b4fee3c270f1f989db43.webm?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >萌系角色陪你烧脑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一众可爱的角色中任选其一，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让他们陪你一起快乐练习数学、轻松通关！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/cec55d092518c8fe6bd0e7609785be86.poster.avif?t=1765408980\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351640/extras/cec55d092518c8fe6bd0e7609785be86.webm?t=1765408980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >出自业界大佬之手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时间试炼》由多位资深游戏人联合打造，团队成员曾参与《Deemo II》《节奏狂热IIDX》等知名作品，更来自迪士尼、科乐美等顶尖游戏公司。</p>",
